<core:FragmentDefinition xmlns:layout="sap.ui.layout" xmlns:core= "sap.ui.core" xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form" 
xmlns="sap.m">
<Dialog id="updateLeave" title="Update Leave Details" >
        <f:SimpleForm>
            <Label text="EmployeeId" />
            <Input id="inputEmployeeID" width="300px" editable="true"/>
            <Label text="LeaveStartDate"/>
            <Input id="inputLeaveStartDate" width="300px" editable="true" type="Date"/>
            <Label text="LeaveEndDate"/>
            <Input id="inputLeaveEndDate" width="300px" editable="true" type="Date"/>
            <Label text="LeaveType"/>
            <Input id="inputLeaveType" width="300px" editable="true"/>
            <Label text="Reason" />
            <Input id="inputReason" width="300px" editable="true"/>
            <Label text="Status" />
            <Input id="inputStatus" width="300px" editable="true"/>
        </f:SimpleForm>
    <footer>
        <Toolbar>
            <ToolbarSpacer/>
                <Button text="Update" press="onUpdateDialog"></Button>
                <Button text="Close" press="onCancleDialog"></Button>
        </Toolbar>
    </footer>
</Dialog>
</core:FragmentDefinition>